    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessemus nos domnus
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2004" key="#Marquis/duke">Romvvald</persName> summus
                        summus <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> gentis Langobardorum, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3631" key="#Actionarii/actores">Annuni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Actionarii/actores">attionario</rs> nostro, tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/3608" key="#Abbots">Theodoraci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> nostro qui in <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3416" key="#Churches">Sancto Petro ad Aqua
                            Sancti Potiti</orgName> deservire visuhis, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >filiis quoddam <name ref="Iohannes Dalmatinus">Iohanni
                            Dalmatini</name>, id est <name ref="Zillone">Zillone</name> et <name
                                ref="Warnicausus">Warnecauso</name>, <name ref="Stephanus"
                                >Stephano</name> seu et <name ref="Therferada">Therferada</name> cum
                                <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                                >terrola</rs></rs> in quantum habere visi sunt, qui fuerunt <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">coloni</rs> nostri de <rs key="#Subactio"
                            >subactionem</rs> nominati Annuni <rs key="#Actionarii/actores"
                            >attionario</rs> nostro et habitare videntur in loco qui nominatur
                        Gratiano, quatenus ab hodierno die habeas et possedeas tam tu qui supra
                        Theodoraci abbas quanque et posterisque tuis qui in ipsum nominato
                        venerabilis locum deservierint, et a nullus quempiam hominem nunquam
                        habeatis aliquando aliquam questionem aut reprehensionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus per hunc nostrum firmissimum preceptum ipsis iam dictis filiis
                        quoddam Iohannis una cum omnia eorum pertinentiam securiter et firmiter
                        habere et possidere valeatis. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione
                        nominate potestati dictavi ego <persName ref="#people/3454"
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer">Persus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vice dominus et referendarii</rs> tibi
                            <persName ref="#people/3613" key="#Notary">Warnecauso</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> scribendum. Acto in <placeName
                            ref="#places/3471" key="#Villages/settlements">Borfaniana</placeName>
                        mense magio per indictione septima. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
